BKM-Analytics

Cemal

6 Mart 2019

In this document, we parse BKM web site for monthly transactions by transaction type and analyze the data for January 2017.

Getting raw data from BKM web page

raw_html <- read_html("https://bkm.com.tr/secilen-aya-ait-sektorel-gelisim/?filter_year=2017&filter_month=1&List=Listele")
raw_html

df_raw <- tables_list[[4]]
df_raw <- df_raw %>% slice(-(1:2))
colnames(df_raw)
## [1] "X1" "X2" "X3" "X4" "X5"
colnames(df_raw) <- c("type", "txn_cc","txn_dc", "tl_cc","tl_dc")
df_raw %>% filter(type != "TOPLAM") %>% mutate_at(vars(txn_cc:tl_dc),funs(gsub("\\.","",.))) %>% mutate_at(vars(txn_cc:tl_dc),funs(gsub(",",".",.))) %>% tbl_df()

Bar chart of transactions by credit card

ggplot(card_df, aes(x=reorder(type,txn_cc),y=txn_cc/10^6,fill=type)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  theme_minimal() + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90,hjust = 1,vjust = 0.5,size = 6),legend.position = "none") + 
  labs(x="",y="Credit Card Txn Count", title="Credit Card transactions count by purchasing type")

Bar chart of transactions by credit card cost

ggplot(card_df, aes(x=reorder(type,tl_cc),y=tl_cc,fill=type)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  theme_minimal() + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90,hjust = 1,vjust = 0.5,size = 6),legend.position = "none") + 
  labs(x="",y="Credit Card TL Count/in TL", title="Credit Card TL count by purchasing type")

Bar chart of transactions by credit card unit cost

ggplot(card_df, aes(x=reorder(type,(tl_cc_unit=tl_cc*10^6/txn_cc)),y=(tl_cc_unit=tl_cc*10^6/txn_cc),fill=type)) + 
  geom_bar(stat="identity") + 
  theme_minimal() + 
  theme(axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 90,hjust = 1,vjust = 0.5,size = 6),legend.position = "none") + 
  labs(x="",y="Credit Card Unit Costs Count/ in TL", title="Credit Card Unit Costs count by purchasing type")

BKM

In this document, we parse BKM web site for monthly transactions by transaction type and analyze the data for

Getting raw data from BKM webpage

raw_tables <- read_html("https://bkm.com.tr/secilen-aya-ait-sektorel-gelisim/?filter_year=2018&filter_month=3&List=Listele") %>% html_table(fill = TRUE)

Processing of raw data

df_raw <- raw_tables[[4]] %>% tbl_df()
colnames(df_raw) <- c("type","txn_cc","txn_dc","tl_cc","tl_dc")
df_raw <- df_raw %>% slice(-(1:2))
cards_df <- 
  df_raw %>% 
  filter(type != "TOPLAM") %>% 
  mutate_at(vars(txn_cc:tl_dc),funs(gsub("\\.","",.))) %>% 
  mutate_at(vars(txn_cc:tl_dc),funs(as.numeric(gsub(",","\\.",.)))) %>% tbl_df() 
## Warning: funs() is soft deprecated as of dplyr 0.8.0
## please use list() instead

## # Before:
## funs(name = f(.)
## 
## # After: 
## list(name = ~f(.))
## This warning is displayed once per session.
